snippet.title: Version 1.5 Teaser - "Astra-nomical Moment" | Zenless Zone Zero
snippet.description:
Under the light, she creates melodies that intertwine, and every thought in this moment becomes a song.
Under the light, she plays the galaxy's message and embraces the hope brought by happiness.
Like an incredible miracle, radiant and dazzling, that illuminates the world.

—Welcome to New Eridu!—
PS5™/iOS/Android/PC | Version 1.4 "A Storm of Falling Stars" of Zenless Zone Zero, HoYoverse's urban fantasy ARPG, is out now: https://hoyo.link/6SOkFDAL
